BSC.desc: TrustFi is committed to provide decentralized BaaS (Blockchain-as-a-Service) solutions for DeFi market based on multichain environments. A complete set of product portfolios developed by TrustFi, including Decentralized Community Driven Incubator (TrustFi Booster), IDO General Protocol with an insured mechanism (TrustFi LaunchPad) and Automated Farm Pools (AFP) Contract (TrustFi Farmer), which is an important supplement to the DeFi infrastructure built on Web 3.0.

CheersLand is a scalable GameFi Metaverse Aggregator where anyone can monetize their gaming experiences and social networks and let games earn diversified rewards through skill-based gameplay and contributions to the ecosystem. This is GameFi-as-a-Service (GaaS) Model, driven by Play-to-Earn and Build-to-Earn mechanics with the product portfolio of Gamified Launchpad, Multi-game Universe, Multi-asset Staking Platform, and NFT Market. CheersLand is owned and governed by $CHEERS Holders.
Kommunitas is the first tierless launchpad on polygon ecosytem.

MetaverseX is a decentralized virtual world sandbox building game that supports NFT creation and trading and Play To Earn mode. Anyone can own virtual land in the sandbox world, design and create various buildings and virtual items, and realize the auction and exchange of virtual items through NFT.
Luna-Pad is peer to peer innovative Launchpad to launch new projects in TerraLuna ecosystem & Binance smart chain.

$METAP: It is the most revolutionary and advanced version of the playable (Metaverse game) system based entirely on artificial intelligence and project that will bring a big change on Metaverse Gaming space both on Mobile and PC. Our ambition is to build a leading NFT+GAMEFİ ecosystem in the blockchain space that delivers sustainable values to our users and investors.

Duet protocol is a multi-chain synthetic assets ecosystem, producing various pegging assets from stock, index, ETF, commodities or any assets with a price feed on blockchain. Duet aims to allow all Web3 residents to allocate funds to any asset with just one crypto wallet.

The engagement between a VIP and the community is sometimes impossible and social networks are not always the solution. However, Peoplez is here to provide an experience where you can be part of something that actually is possible. Peoplez offers total involvement where you, the fan can finally touch something concrete and have interaction with your idols, which seemed impossible until now. We create personal tokens of the most popular artists in the world and give unique opportunities to the users of our platform. They have exclusive interaction possibilities, and can also buy the VIP’s NFT and memorabilia. The Peoplez platform allows you to invest in emerging idols around the world within the music, artistic, and sports arenas.

OrtJob is a new blockchain platform powered by DeFi and self governing DAO created to actualize these two dreams as it delivers freelance jobs based on a secure, decentralized technology. Freelancers will have a vast variety of job options as well as payment methods to choose from. It allows users transparency as they can look at detailed reviews and descriptions of the employer and freelancer. The greatest benefit of this platform has to be that there is NO COMMISSION, meaning users will not be skimped out of any hard worked money.

MetaFighter is a skill-based Play-to-Earn fighting game which captures the essence of arcade fighting classics like Street Fighter, Virtua Fighter and Soul Calibur, while delivering an in-game economy that rewards players for their combat prowess.

Dx Spot is an AI application for trading on crypto exchanges, Decentralized wallet, Gamefi, NFT & DeFi. Dx Spot creates DXS Tokens for utilities in its ecosystem. DXS tokens can be used for the Dx Spot application ecosystem such as subscription fees, top up fuel gas, buy character for playing game, and staking.

MetaChess is the first 3D multiplayer play-to-earn (P2E) and NFT metaverse chess game. The platform is in 2D and 3D. The 3D version will be divided into two. The first part is the regular chess game, with the traditional chess pieces in 3D. The second part is more animated and fancy. It consists of chess pieces in the form of human characters. Watch trailer here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E1VIPs7nigk. You can own NFTs (unique chess pieces) which will be used in the game. The platform also has play-to-earn (P2E) models that makes it worth players’ time. The 2D version is currently playable. You can either play with AI or play with another user.
Scorefam is a P2E & NFT-based sport gaming platform where users earn by predicting and staking, engaging in the football fantasy league and trading NFT player cards with ease.

Discover the Nomadland Island, buy land, build farms , produce mystic flames, battle epic monsters and carnivore plants, capture and train the captured monsters and carnivore plants, evolve in rank and produce new weapons and armours, fight in Arena against other players- in this blockchain based NFT’s Action RPG & strategy game built on Unreal Engine Come dive into the NOMADLAND universe, WIN tokens as you play!

RacewayX is a multi-chain NFT driven strategy-based car racing game with blockchain-powered economy and prize pool redistribution contracts. Players can earn either by playing the game or owning parts of the game with ownable parts of the game in the form of verifiable NFTs.  The gameplay is purely based on physics and player strategy with no physical controls. To play the game, you will need to own a car NFT, selecting a racetrack and ensure you have or buy the required level of gas for the race, choose your race strategy, and view the results.

Monopolon is a GameFi project with a dynamic similar to that of the iconic game ‘Monopoly’. Individual NFTs represent players in ‘board’ where they can move around to earn rewards, join guilds, engage other players in battle (PvP), and participate in boss raids and guild wars on a grand scale. Monopolon also has virtual land and infrastructure that players can purchase to build up equity and secure their place in the metaverse.

The platform also has play-to-earn (P2E) models that makes it worth players’ time. The 2D version is currently playable. You can either play with AI or play with another user.

RacewayX is a multi-chain NFT driven strategy-based car racing game with blockchain-powered economy and prize pool redistribution contracts.
